## Infrastructure Gaps

| Gap | Impact | Fix |
|-----|--------|-----|
| `api.ts` has ZERO timeout/AbortController | Requests hang forever on timeout endpoints | Add 10s AbortController to all fetch calls |
| No error boundary on widgets | One failing fetch crashes the widget | Add try/catch + fallback UI per widget |
| No retry logic | Transient failures = permanent broken state | Add 1-retry with 3s backoff |
| Signals endpoint returns empty [] | SignalsCenter has nothing to show | Investigate: no checker populates `/signals` |
| Narrative endpoint does heavy compute | 15s+ blocking call in request handler | Add caching or background polling |

